  "texts": [
    "Landmark Cooccurrence Generation.",
    "Based on the extracted navigational sequential landmarks, we can further obtain landmark cooccurrence priors from ChatGPT.",
    "Specifically, we pre-define 2 task examples for ChatGPT to generate cooccurrences.",
    "One task example followed by the prompt is as follows:Tell me 3 co-occurrences of bedroom: 1.bed; 2.mirror; 3.nightstand; Tell me 3 co-occurrences of U la k: where U la k is the k-th landmark in an instruction.",
    "We constrain ChatGPT to generate visible objects or scenes rather than abstract objects (e.g., wind) as cooccurrences by stating it explicitly in the prompt."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}